<p>In binary arithmetic, the binary expansion of a <a href=3D"https://en.wi=
kipedia.org/wiki/Fraction" title=3D"Fraction">fraction</a>  <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Repeating_decimal" title=3D"Repeating decimal">te=
