<p>The result is 1197<sub>10</sub>. The first Prior Value of 0 is simply an=
 initial decimal value. This method is an application of the <a href=3D"htt=
ps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Horner_scheme" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Ho=
rner scheme">Horner scheme</a>.
</p>
